-- Total Boosts Stake in Russia’s Novatek to 15%, CFO Says
-- B y   T a r a   P a t e l
-- 2012-06-14T11:03:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-14/total-boosts-stake-in-russia-s-novatek-to-15-cfo-says.html
(Corrects amount purchased to 0.3 percent in second
paragraph of story initially published April 27.)  Total SA (FP)  boosted its stake in OAO
Novatek to 15 percent, according to Chief Financial Officer
Patrick de la Chevardiere.  The French oil company acquired about 0.3 percent of
Novatek on the market for about $120 million, he said on a
conference call on first-quarter earnings.  “There is no emergency” to reach a 19 percent holding, de
la Chevardiere said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tara Patel in Paris at 
